lyrics:
[verse]
In shadows I wander, a soul detached
Lost in the void, where pain hatched
The world blurs, my senses fade
Dissociation, my twisted escapade

[chorus]
Into the abyss, I'm drawn so deep
Aching heart, inside it weeps
Tormented by existence, I silently scream
In this coldwave of life, I drown in my dream
